n-US |access-date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Himself\n|[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n|Voice only\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2018\n|[[Shark Week|''Shark Week's 50 Best Bites:'' \"Monster Tag\"]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://whdh.com/sports/rob-gronkowski-to-appear-on-shark-weeks-monster-tag/ |title=Rob Gronkowski to appear on Shark Week\u2019s \u2018Monster Tag\u2019 |last=Wood |first=Ryan |website=WHDH |language=en |access-date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n|[[Discovery Channel]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Also executive producer\n|-\n|''Unsportsmanlike Comedy with Rob Gronkowski''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2018/01/gronk-rob-gronkowski-liam-neeson-showtime-comedy-special-video-parody-patriots-nfl |title=Gronk promotes upcoming comedy special with video |last=Joseph |first=Andrew |date=January 3, 2018 |website=USA TODAY |language=en-US |access-date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n|[[Showtime (TV network)|Showtime]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2019\n|[[2019 Kids' Choice Sports|''Kids' Choice Sports'']]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20190711005890/en/Nickelodeon%E2%80%99s-Kids%E2%80%99-Choice-Sports-2019-Winners-Release |title=Nickelodeon\u2019s Kids\u2019 Choice Sports 2019 Winners Release |date=2019-07-12 |website=www.businesswire.com |language=en |access-date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n|Himself / Team captain\n|Nickelodeon\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Shop]]''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2852306-highlights-of-rob-gronkowski-kevin-love-cj-mccollum-on-hbos-the-shop |title=Highlights of Rob Gronkowski, Kevin Love, CJ McCollum on HBO's 'The Shop' |last=Polacek |first=Scott |date=September 4, 2019 |website=Bleacher Report |language=en |access-date=2019-12-23}}</ref>\n|Himself\n|[[HBO]]\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013present\n|''[[Fox NFL|NFL on Fox]]''\n|Football analyst\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Fox\n|<ref name=\":9\" />\n|-\n|2019\n|''Fox's New Year's Eve with Steve Harvey''\n|Host\n|<ref name=\":11\">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/fox-new-years-eve-with-steve-harvey-2019-preformers-co-hosts-ymca-world-record-attempt-1202813882/|title=\u2018Fox\u2019s New Year\u2019s Eve With Steve Harvey\u2019 Unveils Performers, Co-Hosts & \u2018YMCA\u2019 World-Record Attempt|last=Pedersen|first=Erik|last2=Pedersen|first2=Erik|date=2019-12-19|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-01-03}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2020\n|''[[Gordon Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell and Back]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Himself\n|Episode: \"The Park Restaurant & Bar\"\n|-\n|''[[WWE SmackDown]]''\n|[[Fox Sports 1]]\n|<ref name=\":10\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/wrestlemania-36/article/wrestlemania-36-two-night-wwe-network-rob-gronkowski-host|title=Unprecedented two-night WrestleMania to be hosted by Rob Gronkowski on WWE Network|website=WWE|language=en|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[The Masked Singer (American TV series)|The Masked Singer]]''\n|White Tiger\n|[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n|Eliminated in Episode 10 of Season 3<ref name=\":11\" />\n|-\n|''[[WrestleMania 36]]''\n|Host\n|[[WWE Network]]\n|Pay-per-view\n|-\n|''Game On!''\n|Team captain\n|[[CBS]]\n|Also executive producer<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/cbs-orders-game-on-keegan-michael-key-venus-williams-rob-gronkowski-1202779075/ |title=\u2018Game On!\u2019: Keegan-Michael Key, Venus Williams & Rob Gronkowski Join CBS Remake Of James Corden\u2019s BAFTA-Winning \u2018A League Of Their Own\u2019 |last=Kanter |first=Jake |date=2019-11-06 |website=Deadline |language=en |access-date=2020-02-11}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|\"[[Swish Swish]]\"\n|[[Katy Perry]] feat. [[Nicki Minaj]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.masslive.com/patriots/2017/08/new_england_patriots_te_rob_gr_11.html |title=New England Patriots TE Rob Gronkowski makes cameo in bizarre Katy Perry music video |last=O'Malley |first=Nick |date=2017-08-24 |website=MassLive |language=en 