019-12-23}}</ref>\n|Himself\n|[[HBO]]\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013present\n|''[[Fox NFL|NFL on Fox]]''\n|Football analyst\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Fox\n|<ref name=\":9\" />\n|-\n|2019\n|''Fox's New Year's Eve with Steve Harvey''\n|Host\n|<ref name=\":11\">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/fox-new-years-eve-with-steve-harvey-2019-preformers-co-hosts-ymca-world-record-attempt-1202813882/|title=\u2018Fox\u2019s New Year\u2019s Eve With Steve Harvey\u2019 Unveils Performers, Co-Hosts & \u2018YMCA\u2019 World-Record Attempt|last=Pedersen|first=Erik|last2=Pedersen|first2=Erik|date=2019-12-19|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2020-01-03}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2020\n|''[[Gordon Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell and Back]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Himself\n|Episode: \"The Park Restaurant & Bar\"\n|-\n|''[[WWE SmackDown]]''\n|[[Fox Sports 1]]\n|<ref name=\":10\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wrestlemania/wrestlemania-36/article/wrestlemania-36-two-night-wwe-network-rob-gronkowski-host|title=Unprecedented two-night WrestleMania to be hosted by Rob Gronkowski on WWE Network|website=WWE|language=en|access-date=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[The Masked Singer (American TV series)|The Masked Singer]]''\n|White Tiger\n|[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n|Eliminated in Episode 10 of Season 3<ref name=\":11\" />\n|-\n|''[[WrestleMania 36]]''\n|Host\n|[[WWE Network]]\n|Pay-per-view\n|-\n|''Game On!''\n|Team captain\n|[[CBS]]\n|Also executive producer<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/cbs-orders-game-on-keegan-michael-key-venus-williams-rob-gronkowski-1202779075/ |title=\u2018Game On!\u2019: Keegan-Michael Key, Venus Williams & Rob Gronkowski Join CBS Remake Of James Corden\u2019s BAFTA-Winning \u2018A League Of Their Own\u2019 |last=Kanter |first=Jake |date=2019-11-06 |website=Deadline |language=en |access-date=2020-02-11}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|\"[[Swish Swish]]\"\n|[[Katy 